videos.description: Kentucky's Isaiah Briscoe gets the steal and Malik Monk chases down the loose ball and makes the layup.
videos.headline: Kentucky knocks the ball free and Monk gets the hustle layup

videos.description: Isiah Briscoe misses the 3-pointer but Kentucky gets the rebound and  it leads to a dunk for Wenyen Gabriel.
videos.headline: Kentucky gets offensive rebound that leads to Gabriel dunk

videos.description: De'Aaron Fox finds the cutting Malik Monk for the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Malik Monk rises up and jams home the alley-oop

videos.description: De'Aaron Fox with crossover leaves defender on the court and Malik Monk hits the 3-pointer for Kentucky.
videos.headline: De'Aaron Fox with the great crossover leads to  Monk 3 pointer

videos.description: Kentucky head coach John Calipari on his teams 1st half performance.
videos.headline: Kentucky head coach John Calipari on his teams 1st half performance

videos.description: LSU's Duop Reath gets the steal and Antonio drives all the way for the layup.
videos.headline: LSU gets the steal and it leads to Blakeny layup

videos.description: Isaiah Briscoe throws the lob to Edrice Adebayo for the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Adebayo hammers home the alley-oop

videos.description: Despite beating LSU 92-85, Kentucky head coach John Calipari was not pleased with the effort of his players and warns them to be ready for a long practice.
videos.headline: Calipari issues stern warning to his Kentucky players

videos.description: Kentucky's Wenyen Gabriel says he's happy with the win but knows the team needs to get better for March.
videos.headline: UK's Gabriel breaks down his team's performance in win

videos.description: Breaking down Kentucky's 92-85 win over LSU
videos.headline: Breaking down Kentucky's 92-85 win over LSU

videos.description: In a much-needed win for Kentucky, Wenyen Gabriel and Malik Monk each score 23 points as No. 15 Kentucky tops LSU 92-85.
videos.headline: Kentucky comes out on top against LSU
